Whether you’re a small business or a large company, we simplify accounting so you can focus on business growth.<br>At Abstract Auditing, we provide comprehensive bookkeeping, accounting, internal auditing, external audit, feasibility study, strategic financial advisory services, tax compliance, and payroll services to meet the needs of startups, SMEs, and established enterprises alike.<br><br>Whether you need help organizing daily transactions or developing a long-term financial plan, our team of experienced chartered accountants ensures accuracy, compliance, and clarity every step of the way.</p><p>Get in touch with our team today for expert support you can count on.</p>								</div>

				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ's)</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2015b46 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="2015b46" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">What is the difference between accounting and bookkeeping?
</h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9209a20 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="9209a20" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									Bookkeeping is about recording day-to-day financial transactions like invoices and expenses. Accounting goes a step further. It interprets, analyzes, and reports financial data to help with business decision-making and compliance.
 								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-7621af8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="7621af8" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Why should I work with a Dubai bookkeeping and accounting company?

</h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ddae2b4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="ddae2b4" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Employing a local bookkeeping and accounting company ensures that you work with an accounting team of professionals who are aware of UAE rules and regulations. You will save time that you can use to reinvest in your company, keep in compliance, stay out of trouble, and make financial success.</p>								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-e1a507e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="e1a507e" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Do Dubai's accounting services qualify for tax deductions?
</h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f75634e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="f75634e" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									Yes, you can deduct accounting and auditing services from your taxable income since they are typically regarded as business expenses. Our tax consultants can help ensure everything is properly documented and filed.
 								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-a777651 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="a777651" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Do I need an accountant for VAT in the UAE?
</h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-131a5d0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="131a5d0" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									VAT laws in the UAE can be complex, and penalties for errors are steep. An experienced accountant will help you register correctly, file returns on time, and stay compliant with Federal Tax Authority (FTA) regulations.
								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-625bc6f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="625bc6f" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">How often should bookkeeping be done?
</h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-463a0c7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="463a0c7" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									Ideally, bookkeeping should be done on a weekly or monthly basis to ensure accuracy. To keep your records up to date without interfering with your workflow, we provide customizable timetables.
   								</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d87387f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="d87387f" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
					<h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Is outsourcing accounting services in Dubai preferable?
</h3>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f82028e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="f82028e" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									Outsourcing to a trusted accounting firm like Abstract Auditing saves you time, reduces overhead costs, and gives you access to experienced professionals, without the overhead of a full-time in-house team.
								</div>
				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
